; Mailman character — composed from primitives so it reads as the reference
; image's blue-uniformed postie with a red mail bag.
;   Cap (blue prism)         on top
;   Head (skin-tone sphere)  beneath cap
;   Torso (blue box)         shirt
;   Belt (cream stripe)      thin ring
;   Legs (dark blue boxes)   below belt
;   Bag  (red box on strap)  at hip on +Z (the side facing forward as the
;                            player walks "right" in screen space)

